- Extend interpreter identification to recognize versioned interpreter names (e.g. via regex patterns like the ones already used in `exec-safe-bin-runtime-policy.ts`).
- Apply the same logic in both `findInterpreterSpec` (inline-eval detection) and `isInterpreterLikeAllowlistPattern` (persistence gate), so that resolved versioned basenames like `python3.14` are treated as interpreter-like.

